Package: hwglabr
Title: Collection of R functions used in the Hochwagen Lab
Version: 0.2
Authors@R: c(
  person("Luis", "Vale-Silva", email = "luisvalesilva@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Tovah", "Markowitz", email = "tem298@nyu.edu", role = "aut"),
  person("Neem", "Patel", email = "njp301@nyu.edu ", role = "ctb")
  )
Description: Compilation of functions written and used frequently by Hochwagen
    lab members. This means mostly functions used to analyse data from ChIP-seq
    experiments: wiggle data produced by the lab's Fastq2Peak ChIP-seq  analysis
    pipeline.
Suggests:
    dplyr,
    marray,
    pbapply,
    readr,
    scales
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.1)
